---
title: Sweet and Sour Pork with Mango, Ginger and Basmati Rice
description: Tangy vinegar, savoury soy sauce, and spicy ginger make up the base to this non-traditional sweet and sour sauce. Sweet bell pepper and mango elevate this revamped take-out dish even further.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-and-sour-pork-8b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/sweet-and-sour-pork-8b4567.pdf
servings: 2
course: main course
